    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "Thanks VVO - one doubt though, below is our code where can we put that?\r\n\r\n-- --\r\n\r\n```js\r\n//CLOSE AND CLEAR\r\n$('body #header-main .icon-close').on('click tap', function() {\r\n  $('#header-search-form input#search')\r\n    .val('')\r\n    .focus()\r\n    .trigger({ type: 'keypress', which: 13 });\r\n  $('body').removeClass('search-init search-active filter-active');\r\n  $('#header-shopping-cart a.icon-cart').delay(300).queue(function(next) {\r\n    $('#header-shopping-cart a.icon-cart').css({ 'z-index': '1' });\r\n    next();\r\n  });\r\n});\r\n```",
